  <summary date="2021-05-24T18:02:06Z" status="Introduced in House">Ensuring Economic Recovery Act

 This bill requires the Small Business Administration to report on the recovery of small businesses from the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) pandemic and the effects on small businesses of increasing the federal minimum hourly wage to $15.</summary>
